description:
*Remember Columbine: Interview with Rachel's father, Darrell Scott* | Have you ever walked into a situation and wondered where God was in all of it? We have the honor of getting to interview Darrell Scott about his daughter and the ministry that came out of her death from the Columbine school shooting. Rachel's Challenge has been shared with millions of students nation-wide and has led thousands to the LORD.
